    "summary": {
      "text": "Customers find this dog bed to be of high quality and appreciate its softness, with one noting the sides are fluffy but firm. The bed is spacious and comfortable, with one customer mentioning it's perfect for their soon-to-be large lab puppies. Customers praise its durability, noting it holds up well on delicate cycles, and find it easy to wash and worth the price.",
