          "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/81-GWjUgeBL._SY88.jpg"
        ],
        "helpful_votes": "5 people found this helpful"
      },
      {
        "position": 5,
        "title": "Terrific buy for nice bed.",
        "text": "Recently adopted a 70 pound service dog and didn’t realize how big of a bed was needed until I saw her hanging off of the 36” round bed I already had at home. I was worried the egg crate foam would be too hard but it’s not too bad. My girl crawled into the bed shortly after I put it down on the floor and she seems to enjoy having the edge to lay her head on. I came downstairs yesterday morning and noticed the cat was sleeping in the corner of the bed - and we all know how picky cats are about their comfort. It’s quite thick but not very heavy so it’s easy to move around. Hopefully it will wash well and stand up to the test of time. All in all a good buy if you need a BIG bed for your pup.",
        "rating": 5,
        "date": "September 23, 2025",
